name: Imugi
shortLoreBlurb: Imugi is a creature from Korea associated with proto-dragon, rivers. Stories warn that respect for waters and their spirits is essential.
overlapsLinks: Fafnir (Norse), Jörmungandr (Norse), Manannán mac Lir (Celtic), Naga (India/SE Asia), Poseidon (Greek), Quetzalcoatl (Aztec), Tangaroa (Polynesian), Yemaya (Yoruba)
